les in that database. If this value is specified without units, it is taken as seconds. The default is one minute (1min). This parameter can only be set in the postgresql.conf file or on the server command line.\n```\n\n## autovacuum_naptime \u6e90\u7801\u5206\u6790\n\n\u6839\u636e\u5b98\u65b9\u6587\u6863\u611f\u89c9\u4e86\u89e3\u603b\u662f\u4e0d\u5f7b\u5e95\uff0c\u4e0b\u9762\u6839\u636e\u4ee3\u7801\u5206\u6790\u4e00\u4e0b\u8be5\u53c2\u6570\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1741340554, "style": "", "script": "<script src='/assets/GmeekTOC.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5057571?s=96&v=4", "createdDate": "2025-03-07", "dateLabelColor": "#0969da"}, "P10": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/pg_rewind-wei-shen-me-xu-yao-kai-qi-wal_log_hins.html", "labels": ["wal_log_hints", "pg_rewind"], "postTitle": "pg_rewind\u4e3a\u4ec0\u4e48\u9700\u8981\u5f00\u542f wal_log_hins", "postUrl": "post/pg_rewind-wei-shen-me-xu-yao-kai-qi-wal_log_hins.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/swrd/swrd.github.io/issues/10", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 5520, "description": "## \u4e00\u3001`wal_log_hints`\u53c2\u6570\u4f5c\u7528\n\n### \uff08\u4e00\uff09Hint bits\u673a\u5236\u6982\u8ff0\n\n\u5728PostgreSQL\u4e2d\uff0cHint bits\u662f\u4e00\u79cd\u7528\u4e8e\u4f18\u5316\u6027\u80fd\u7684\u91cd\u8981\u673a\u5236\uff0c\u5b83\u5b58\u50a8\u5728\u5143\u7ec4\uff08tuple\uff09\u5934\u90e8\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1747381922, "style": "", "script": "<script src='/assets/GmeekTOC.js'></script>", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5057571?s=96&v=4", "createdDate": "2025-05-16", "dateLabelColor": "#0969da"}, "P11": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/shen-ru-tan-suo-PostgreSQL-18-de-xin-te-xing.html", "labels": ["\u65b0\u7248\u672c\u7279\u6027", "PG18"], "postTitle": "\u6df1\u5165\u63a2\u7d22 PostgreSQL 18 \u7684\u65b0\u7279\u6027", "postUrl": "post/shen-ru-tan-suo-PostgreSQL-18-de-xin-te-xing.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/swrd/swrd.